      "helpText": "The current processing status of this facility.  ACTIVE  status indicates the facility is participating in transmitting data to the CMOP.  INACTIVE status indicates that CMOP processing is not  currently available.  'N' for 'Active Non-CS only'  'C' for 'Active CS only'  'B' for 'Active both CS and Non-CS' ",
